<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>碎碎念 - 标签 - STARRY-S' Blog</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/tags/%E7%A2%8E%E7%A2%8E%E5%BF%B5/</link><description>碎碎念 - 标签 - STARRY-S' Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>hxstarrys@gmail.com (STARRY-S)</managingEditor><webMaster>hxstarrys@gmail.com (STARRY-S)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 02 Jan 2023 01:20:31 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.starry-s.moe/tags/%E7%A2%8E%E7%A2%8E%E5%BF%B5/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Hello 2023</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/hello-2023/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Jan 2023 01:20:31 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2023/hello-2023/</guid><description>&lt;p>2023 新年快乐。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hello 2022</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/hello-2022/</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jan 2022 01:09:24 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2022/hello-2022/</guid><description>&lt;p>又到了写年终总结的时候了，说实话今年发生了好多好多好多的事情，我可能要写很久才能把这些事全写完。然而我文笔不好，回忆事情容易写成流水帐，所以不重要的事情我只好简短略过一下。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hello 2021</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2021/hello-2021/</link><pubDate>Wed, 06 Jan 2021 01:57:19 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2021/hello-2021/</guid><description>&lt;p>本来我已经戴好耳机准备睡觉了的，突然想起来2020年的年终总结还没有写，恰好脑子里有想写的东西，于是大概构思了一下，便从床上爬起来开灯打开电脑开写年终总结。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hello 2019</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2019/hello-2019/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jan 2019 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2019/hello-2019/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>Hello 2018</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2018/hello-2018/</link><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2018 22:58:06 +0000</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2018/hello-2018/</guid><description><![CDATA[<p><figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/2018/hello-2018/images/5cm_per_second.jpg" title="秒速5厘米" data-thumbnail="/posts/2018/hello-2018/images/5cm_per_second.jpg" data-sub-html="<h2> </h2><p>秒速5厘米</p>">
        
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption"> </figcaption>
    </figure></p>]]></description></item><item><title>Sorry, Thank you.</title><link>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2016/sorry-thankyou/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Nov 2016 15:00:24 +0800</pubDate><author>STARRY-S</author><guid>https://blog.starry-s.moe/posts/2016/sorry-thankyou/</guid><description>&lt;p>想了很久不知道以什么来作为本篇文章的开头，不确定自己真的想说些什么，但是我还是带着确切目的来写这篇文章的。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这一个月发生了一些不太愉快的事，可能不算很大吧但是对我来说这个影响真的很大。我不知道应该从何说起，先静下来带上耳机慢慢的想慢慢的写。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>